@startuml
[*] --> DisplayJourneyDetails : user login and destination selection
DisplayJourneyDetails --> ActivateDrivingMode : activate driving mode
ActivateDrivingMode --> SelectPlaceToEat : choose other options
SelectPlaceToEat --> ViewMenu : select a place to eat
ViewMenu --> PlaceOrder : view its menu, and place an order if they are hungry
PlaceOrder --> InformAuthorities : in case of an accident
InformAuthorities --> SendNotifications : send notifications during driving or in case of an accident
SendNotifications --> ProvideFeedback : upon completion of their journey
ProvideFeedback --> [*] : provide feedback

@enduml
